title: How do people not understand picks in high silver/low gold?
body: I am in silver 1 and people are picking fucking taric supp, j4 top (granted j4 is godly but not as top), udyr jung, teemo, garen, etc.  How the fuck do people not know that udyr/teemo/garen is like the most useless team fight champ ever not to mention taric.  Is silver that shitty of a fucking elo?
